values.jungle-1: a village of lizardfolk, who are currently at war with a tribe of bullywugs. The lizardfolk are led by a powerful shaman, who is trying to summon a powerful demon to aid them in the war.
values.jungle-2: a hunting party of grung warriors, who are searching for a rare herb that is said to have powerful healing properties. The grung are willing to trade the herb for a magical artifact that they believe is hidden in the jungle.
